# Pitch2Play Crontab Schedule Example
# Run pitch2play every Sunday at 12:00 PM
# 
# To use this:
# 1. Copy this file: cp crontab.example crontab
# 2. Update the paths to match your setup
# 3. Install to crontab: crontab crontab
# 4. Verify: crontab -l

# Min  Hour  Day   Month DayOfWeek Command
# |    |     |     |     |
# |    |     |     |     +-- Sunday = 0, Monday = 1, ..., Saturday = 6
# |    |     |     +-- Month (1-12)
# |    |     +-- Day (1-31)
# |    +-- Hour (0-23)
# +-- Minute (0-59)

# Run every Sunday at 12:00 PM
0 12 * * 0 cd /path/to/pitch2play && npm start >> /path/to/pitch2play/cron.log 2>&1

# Alternative: Run every day at 8:00 AM
# 0 8 * * * cd /path/to/pitch2play && npm start >> /path/to/pitch2play/cron.log 2>&1

# Alternative: Run every 6 hours
# 0 */6 * * * cd /path/to/pitch2play && npm start >> /path/to/pitch2play/cron.log 2>&1
